channel.title: Moparscape wont open (mac)
channel.description:
I'm really hoping you can help me with this.
I downloaded the mac version, and I try to open the MoparScape.jar, and I get a message saying:
[center]"[b]Jar Launcher[/b][/center]
The jar file 'MoparScape.jar' could not be launched. Check the Console for possible error messages"
I dont know what this means. I opened Console, and didn't see anything. I also tried going to the "open" option in Console. All it did, was let me see the coding, or whatever it is that makes up the program. (Btw, there is no 'run' option in console. All it seems to do is let you see what makes up the program) Can someone please tell me how to get MoparScape to open? I am really anxious to play, but cant due to this... Thanks for the help.
Note: This is on a mac. I read the FAQ, and dont really know what to do on a mac. It only has things for a pc.
Thanks for any help on the matter.
